item.title: Venue
item.description: This conference will be held at the Conference Center of the Kexing Science Park in Nanshan District, Shenzhen. The Kexing International Conference Center is based in the Kexing Science Park—a world-class R&D headquarters, offering six conference halls of various sizes for global enterprises. It provides one-stop conference support services to fully meet the diverse meeting needs. Kexing Science Park is located at the core of Shenzhen’s high-tech park, positioned within a multi-dimensional transport hub close to Shenzhen’s ports, docks, and airport.
